      <talk_question mid="70"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>Well,  I, <FONT color=#a82424>Blacksmith Borin the Great</FONT>, have discovered the greatest <FONT color=#a82424>invention</FONT> of my or any other lifetime.<BR>It's an item that will solve all your problems and worries!<BR>What do you say? Want to know what it is?<BR></html>]]></talk_question>
