      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>Really? Haha.. There's no need for you to feel embarrassed.<BR>Everyone already knows about your <FONT color=#a82424>terrible situation</FONT>.<BR>Come on.. Be honest, you would like to take a peek right?</html>]]></talk_question>
