      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>I'm saying this device will analyzes what is being said and it would judge whether it's a lie or a truth.<BR>It reads <FONT color=#a82424>psychological changes</FONT> as well as <FONT color=#a82424>blood pressure</FONT>, <FONT color=#a82424>pulse</FONT>, and <FONT color=#a82424>breathing</FONT>. It is the epitome of <FONT color=#a82424>advanced digital technology</FONT> based on <FONT color=#a82424>psychology</FONT>, <FONT color=#a82424>microengineering</FONT>, and complex <FONT color=#a82424>wave-motion</FONT> technology. Mwahahaha!</html>]]></talk_question>
