   <talk_paragraph index="n016_trader_borin-2" image="QW_10.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>Of course! If someone's lying to you, do you want the device to make a little beeping sound, or let rip with a blood-curdling death cry? Hahaha!<BR>Now, remember that you need to <FONT color=#a82424>record</FONT> only <FONT color=#a82424>loud and full screams</FONT> over <FONT color=#a82424>100 decibels</FONT>.<BR>From <FONT color=#a82424>Frost Wind Forest</FONT>, record the <FONT color=#a82424>screams</FONT> of <FONT color=#a82424>hounds</FONT>, <FONT color=#a82424>goblins</FONT>, and <FONT color=#a82424>orcs</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
